# Application layer

## Controllers

- Path mirrors URL: `application/controllers/servers/control.php`
- Extend `Controller`, access registry: `$this->registry`, `$this->load`, `$this->user`
- Load models: `$this->load->model('servers')` then `$this->serversModel`

## Models

- File `application/models/foo.php` → class `fooModel extends Model`
- Use `$this->db` for queries (wrapper in `engine/database/mysql.php`)

## Views

- Return HTML via `$this->load->view('path', $vars)`
- Common layout: `common/header`, `common/footer`, `common/admheader`
- Short PHP tags may appear in views

## Config

- Settings in `application/config.example.php` (tracked template)
- Runtime: `application/config.php` (gitignored, created by installer or `cp config.example.php`)
- Payment toggles: `'freekassa' => '1'` etc.

## Payments

Result webhooks: `application/controllers/result/{gateway}.php`
